719789f-a.title: Manhattan: Fort Charles Place - Jacobus Place
719789f-a.text:
Fort Charles Place, north from Jacobus Place to Marble
Hill Avenue, showing the repaving of this thoroughfare
by the Works Progress Administration. This series of
photos is progressive.
